## Demo Program Component Map

| Phase | SCIS File     | Description              | Components (CpIDs)                  |
|-------|--------------|--------------------------|-----------------------------------|
| p0    | p0s0f1.py   | Main Entry Point          | Cp0s0f1.1 (main), Cp0s0f1.2 (init) |
|       | p0s0f2.txt  | File Map                  | Cp0s0f2.1 (list_files), Cp0s0f2.2 (update_map) |
| p1    | p1s0f1.py   | Core Logic A              | Cp1s0f1.1 (process_data), Cp1s0f1.2 (validate_input) |
|       | p1s1f1.py   | Core Logic B              | Cp1s1f1.1 (calculate_result), Cp1s1f1.2 (log_output), Cp1s1f1.3 (cleanup) |
| p2    | p2s0f1.py   | Utility Functions         | Cp2s0f1.1 (helper_one), Cp2s0f1.2 (helper_two) |
|       | p2s1f1.py   | Data Handlers             | Cp2s1f1.1 (load_data), Cp2s1f1.2 (save_data) |
| p3    | p3s0f1.py   | Reporting / Visualization | Cp3s0f1.1 (generate_report), Cp3s0f1.2 (render_chart) |

***

This table illustrates an organized set of files and components using SCIS coordinate and component ID conventions, demonstrating clear modularity and traceability across phases.



